{"id":4210,"date":"2024-12-16T14:50:43","date_gmt":"2024-12-16T14:50:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=4210"},"modified":"2024-12-16T14:50:43","modified_gmt":"2024-12-16T14:50:43","slug":"master-ball-maker","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/master-ball-maker\/","title":{"rendered":"Master Ball Maker (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Cube Corp.<\/strong> &#8211; Standing behind the southwest stall in the Cube Corp. exterior area.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Gives you a Master Ball in exchange for Gems.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>Gems<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>30 Gems<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to Cube Corp. and follow the path west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-main-cube-corp-building.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the main Cube Corp. building. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the main Cube Corp. building.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Master Ball Maker is directly behind stall in the corner here. You\u2019ll see it almost instantly.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/02-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-master-ball-maker.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Master Ball Maker. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Master Ball Maker.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Purpose<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/03-pokemon-unbound-trading-30-gems-for-a-master-ball.jpg\" alt=\"Trading 30 Gems for a Master Ball. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Trading 30 Gems for a Master Ball.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Master Ball Maker can make unlimited Master Balls for you, for a cost of <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/items\/gems\/\">30 Gems of any type<\/a>. <\/p>\n<p>There\u2019s no limit to how many Master Balls you can acquire from this NPC, as long as you have the required number of Gems.<\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\"><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Among the best ways to get Gems is by either farming them as Rock Smash items in the desert, or by <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/items\/mining-items\/\">mining at Crystal Peak<\/a>.<\/div>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Useful NPCs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":4211,"parent":2143,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[],"class_list":["post-4210","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/4210","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"u